title: "An Electrifying New Upgrade for Tesla Leads the Market Higher"
text: "Morgan Stanley NYSE: MS is going all-in on Tesla NASDAQ: TSLA. The firm raised its rating on the stock to Overweight from Equal Weight and set a new price target."

title: "Tesla shares jump after Morgan Stanley predicts Dojo supercomputer could add $500 billion in market value"
text: "Tesla's Dojo supercomputer could fuel a $500 billion jump in the electric vehicle maker's market value
source_name: analysts at Morgan Stanley said in a note Monday."

title: "Apple ETFs in Focus Ahead of iPhone 15 Launch Event"
text: "Apple (APPL) is gearing up for its iPhone launch event at the Steve Jobs Theater in California. The technology giant is set to unveil the iPhone 15 series smartphones
date: as well as the high-end Pro and Pro Max variations."
